    "content": "<p>4\ufe0f\u20e33\ufe0f\u20e3 Here&#39;s the 43rd post highlighting key new features of the upcoming v258 release of systemd. <a href=\"https://mastodon.social/tags/systemd258\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"tag\">#<span>systemd258</span></a></p><p>Back in v257 we added support for RestartMode=debug: if used and a service is automatically restarted due to Restart= a special environment variable DEBUG_INVOCATION=1 is set for the new invocation. This is then supposed to enable special logic in the service code that generates additional debug logging and other behaviour.</p>",
